<Author>eweaver6
<Content>Nice Hotel for the Value We went on a cruise from the Port of Miami and wanted a hotel that was close to the Port. This property is excellant for the value. They allow you to leave your vehicle with no charge. Which is wonderful due to the Port charges $20 per day. The hotel staff is very nice. The only negative aspect is this particular property recommends a shuttle service that will take you to the port for $10 per person, but the shuttle service fails to tell you they can't to round trip service until you have returned from your vacation. If the service had told us that up front then we would not have had to wait 45 minutes to get a cab. I suggest that you call a cab. The price for the cab is a little more, but you won't have to wait when you return for a ride back to your vehicle. 
