<Content>MOTEL 6 ON STEROIDS My next installment in a long line of hotel reviews. Amazingly enough up until now I have never stayed at an extended stayamerica. Greatfully, unless I am terribly hard up I will never stay in one again. This hotel is really a motel. It has the hardest bed I have ever slept on. As expected no one here speaks English but that was anticipated. There was a $70.00 fridge a hot plate and a desk that comes right out of MIKES used furniture. Let me say I have stayed in worse places but for the money this is not worth it. I recommend you spend the extra $100.00 and stay at a nice place. $150.00 is too muchthanksTodd 
